  "title": "Does urbanisation influence agricultural activities? a case study of Andhra Pradesh",
  "abstract": "This paper examines the effect of urbanization on the composition of the agricultural sector in Andhra Pradesh. Findings indicate a larger concentration of high-value food commodities in the urban and peri-urban areas than in the hinterlands/rural areas.",
